Scott, Thanks for the tip. I would also suggest that the a similar modification be applied for the "Edit Users" listing under the admin menu.  To implement this, change the following line in admin/user.php: 
```text
if ($sort == "name") {


    $sort = "firstname";


}
```
 to 
```text
if ($sort == "name") {


    $sort = "laststname";


}
```
 I think this shoud be the default in both cases. Surely sorting by last name is preferable in most circumstances to sorting by first name.

